public interface ObjectByClassPropertySupplier<T> extends PropertySupplier<T,​Class<? extends T>>
This interface is designed to read properties and return single instances. This supplier is supposed to create some object by invocation of default constructor. Resulted object is used as value of the property. The correct format of the property value is fully qualified name of the class.
